# A theater wants to enforce age restrictions for movie tickets.
# Ask the user for their age, and tell them whether they can see G (appropriate for under 13),
# PG-13 (appropriate for 13 to 17), or R (appropriate for over 18) rated movies.'''

# Ask the user for their age whether they can see  
age = int(input("Enter your age: "))
# G (appropriate for under 13), PG-13 (appropriate for 13 to 17), 
if age < 13: 
    print("You can watch G rated movies.")
elif 13 <= age <= 17:
    print("You can watch PG-13 and G rated movies.")
else:
    print("You can watch R, PG-13, and G rated movies.")
